    <w:p w14:paraId="2C078E63" w14:textId="53E0350D" w:rsidR="00361849" w:rsidRDefault="256E9CC7">
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Counting website</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="23AD47E6" w14:textId="7AA79A1D" w:rsidR="36CE701C" w:rsidRDefault="36CE701C">
      <w:r>
        <w:t>General website criteria</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="69869C76" w14:textId="78D51E76" w:rsidR="00DA548E" w:rsidRDefault="00512C8B" w:rsidP="00DA548E">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="0"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">The goal of this website is to replace physical mite click counters. It should be easy to use and have good visual feedback. </w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="59C538DB" w14:textId="5A23B4B2" w:rsidR="00AB41BB" w:rsidRDefault="00AB41BB" w:rsidP="00DA548E">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="0"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">When the user enters the website they should be prompted to pick between three different modes of counting, SWD, mites, and lygus. On click the website should load up those columns. </w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="05CB82C9" w14:textId="6C2D3B86" w:rsidR="256E9CC7" w:rsidRDefault="00DA548E" w:rsidP="00DA548E">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="0"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">Keys on the keyboard to correspond to each category with two modes for data entry. </w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="175C3F51" w14:textId="46316F86" w:rsidR="006555B2" w:rsidRDefault="00FC232F" w:rsidP="006555B2">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="1"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">Each column in the display is its own species, with the top being adult, middle row being nymph, and the bottom being egg. </w:t>
      </w:r>
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="5BA5B436" w14:textId="787B9E60" w:rsidR="00F55BE1" w:rsidRDefault="0093063A" w:rsidP="00F55BE1">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="1"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Alternatively, there should be a mode where the user can hit space to enter Adult mode, enter to enter nymph mode, and shift to enter egg mode. (when in one of the modes, the row should be lightly highlighted</w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="4C092C99" w14:textId="447C4B78" w:rsidR="00F55BE1" w:rsidRDefault="00F55BE1" w:rsidP="00F55BE1">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="0"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Visual Style: The app should be friendly with bright colors. The rows within the columns should clearly show the corresponding entry key to the right of the corresponding photo (each column should have three photos corresponding to the three stages of development) The columns should be their own bubble / box, with some small separation between them. The rows within the columns should also be bubbles, and they should mostly fill the column</w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="6397555D" w14:textId="478FCCEF" w:rsidR="00693DD2" w:rsidRDefault="00693DD2" w:rsidP="00693DD2">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/>
        <w:numPr>
          <w:ilvl w:val="1"/>
          <w:numId w:val="1"/>
        </w:numPr>
      </w:pPr>
      
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">Each row bubble, should contain an image, the name and the key cap corresponding. If the bubble gets clicked it should pop up a more detailed ID specification that remains within the column. </w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="2BDDAD0A" w14:textId="13602ADF" w:rsidR="009B064F" w:rsidRDefault="00F8619E" w:rsidP="00512C8B">
